Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类所说的话 不能全部相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我五名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一 我去市政厅查看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护了小优吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在利用他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往市政厅查看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就来 小优
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是天转阴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是袭击的好天气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
