Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:31.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无法逃离的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:38.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}和谁的内心都无法相系　　　　　　　
