Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an7\fs27\b0\bord1}Αντιο ο κοσμοs μαs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:54.13,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an7}悠久的祈愿
